posts.subject: Epstein found Dead
posts.body:
Disgraced multimillionaire Jeffrey Epstein died overnight of apparent suicide, media outlets are reporting.

The New York Post cited law enforcement sources. 

ABC News and The New York Times also quoted officials as saying that Epstein died in his Manhattan cell. ABC quoted three unidentified officials.

The Times, which said Epstein hanged himself, quoted unidentified officials as saying his body was found at 7:30 a.m. Saturday.

Officials at the Metropolitan Correctional Center did not immediately respond to an email seeking comment on the reported suicide. The New York Fire Department, without naming the individual, confirmed that a person in cardiac arrest was taken from the Metropolitan Correctional Center to the hospital shortly before 7 a.m.
